  "body": "<p>Really enjoyed the first stop on my tour with Spotlight, Christchurch, New Zealand. I've tried numerous times to put the visit into words, but feel it's best to just show the 2 store sessions through photos for now.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"14a-spotlight_chch1-600x400.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599890603296-XHSN1JGOUFS0L3YSX68W/14a-spotlight_chch1-600x400.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"14b-spotlight_chch2-600x400.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599890556900-XQ3EC6VLAMAUHVPD5PLZ/14b-spotlight_chch2-600x400.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"14c-.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599890557470-NFTTE73H3MGWH09KJ2N3/14c-.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"14d-spotlight_chch4-600x400.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599890557464-MTD7J905QBZYPF47G3ZF/14d-spotlight_chch4-600x400.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"14e-spotlight_chch51-600x400.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599890558081-6ATAQOKO84WI6WDBG34C/14e-spotlight_chch51-600x400.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"14f-spotlight_chch6-600x400.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599890558587-ZWPHEIPQ59YDCOZKTAYY/14f-spotlight_chch6-600x400.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"14g-spotlight_chch7-600x449.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599890558825-NN4AUXE9PIUHNWMDCI47/14g-spotlight_chch7-600x449.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"14h-spotlight_chch8-600x400.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599890559304-HQ5PMLCWTRPO19OUQR78/14h-spotlight_chch8-600x400.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"14i-spotlight_chch9-600x400.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599890559402-CD3C4G3LL26HQOWA83G1/14i-spotlight_chch9-600x400.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"14j-spotlight_chch9a-600x400.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599890633920-H2D2NTNX3G7YSNB3SXNL/14j-spotlight_chch9a-600x400.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"14k-spotlight_chch9b-600x400.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599890560800-Z6BXY8IPB358FVRTJXVY/14k-spotlight_chch9b-600x400.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"14l-spotlight_chch9c-600x400.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599890560573-I31OH77W26ZWE52ZTSIH/14l-spotlight_chch9c-600x400.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"14m-spotlight_chch9d-600x400.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599890561340-CKBT0XMEZ68I0RSAQA0Q/14m-spotlight_chch9d-600x400.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"14n-spotlight_chch9e-600x400.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599890562223-6X4CGWYALNPY3BXL908C/14n-spotlight_chch9e-600x400.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"14o-spotlight_chch9f-600x400.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599890562318-YLFIMUC4A9B6I10UPI6T/14o-spotlight_chch9f-600x400.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Thanks to everyone who came from near and far!</p>"
